\begin{frame}[fragile]
  \frametitle{Tweaks}
  LilyPond is almost infinitely configurable.
  All graphical objects you see on the screen have properties that you can override,
  either for just the next object or for the rest of the score.
  Other properties of the score
  (not directly connected to individual grobs)
  are also tweakable.

